          <title>Angels star Mike Trout moving from center to right field in hopes of staying more healthy</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TEMPE, Ariz. (AP) — Los Angeles Angels oft-injured star Mike Trout is moving from center to right field in hopes of better preserving his health. The three-time AL MVP played in 82 or fewer games in three of the past four seasons while dealing with an assortment of injuries.]]></description>
